display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>-structure of weight <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n+k]]></fr:tex> on <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {H}^k(K_A)]]></fr:tex>, i.e. the filtration <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[F]]></fr:tex> is <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[(n+k)]]></fr:tex>-opposite to its complex conjugate (which makes sense, since <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A\subset \mathbb {R}]]></fr:tex>).</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree></fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
